flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Daily start of production planning cycle.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Fetch vehicle build plan forecasts from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Generate daily production schedules using Cortex Auto Forecast.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Safety Stock Service - Allocate capacity across press lines using Safety Stock Service.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[Stream: STREAMS - Calculate raw material and blank requirements using STREAMS.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Handle expedited orders using Remote Functions.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Write back optimized schedules and MRP plans to SAP S/4HANA.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved on-time delivery, decreased working capital, and optimized capacity utilization.]
  N3 -->|Insufficient raw materials detected.| B1[Trigger procurement request via Remote Functions.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Ensure material availability for production.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|High number of urgent orders.| B2[Prioritize urgent orders using CWB Lifecycle.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Optimize COGS impact while meeting critical build requirements.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Unexpected capacity constraints.| B3[Adjust production schedules using Process Builder.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Maintain optimal production flow and minimize disruptions.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]